00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:28,760
Father.

288
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,920
Father, why are you here

289
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,200
at this hour of the night?

290
00:16:38,280 --> 00:16:39,240
Don't tell me

291
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:41,080
