400
00:23:48,600 --> 00:23:49,400
(What should I do?)

401
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,600
(I can't just abandon Xiu.)

402
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:53,480
(But Yu'er...)

403
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,400
(Don't tell me I need)

