548
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:27,159
I have.

549
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,000
I'm fine now.

550
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:32,880
You may begin then.

551
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,600
This is great.

552
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:28,720
